{{IPA notice}}
This article is about the [[phonology]] and [[phonetics]] of the [[Upper Sorbian language]].

==Vowels==
The vowel inventory of Upper Sorbian is exactly the same as that of [[Lower Sorbian]].{{sfnp|Stone|2002|p=600}} It is also very similar to the vowel inventory of [[Slovene language|Slovene]].

{| class="wikitable" cellpadding="4"
|+ Vowel phonemes{{sfnp|Stone|2002|p=600}}{{sfnp|Šewc-Schuster|1984|p=20}}
